sentences: He has mixed albums for Kirk Franklin (Grammy Award winning 2005 release Hero among others), Dorinda Clark Cole, Tye Tribbett, Israel Houghton, Kurt Carr, Hezekiah Walker and Ledisi.
In 2010, Jaszcz started an independent record label, Yosh Bros Entertainment, as a platform for artists he produces.
"Yosh," as he has been nicknamed, currently resides and works in Franklin, Tennessee.
The roster currently includes Kree Woods, DJ Sahnik, and Lacey Mason.
